channel.title: EmperousX V2 [PI]
channel.description:
Hello everyone i'm finally releasing my v2 since 8+ people inboxed me and posted on a few threads asking for it. I had it in my dropbox but now it's gone. so i started off a cleaned out base :)
Now it won't have the sexy, and yet shitty new things released of today, but as i worked on the proejct i wrote down what I added. So enjoy everyone, flaming will be overlooked and not cared for ;)
[SPOILER="Base Updates"]- Cache packed 660 items (with Examined all working but only 653 item models added) - Cache packed 602 npc's - 602 anims/gfx (including Nex, korasi anims and veteran cape emote) - updates interfaces - Supports HD sprites - Supports animated GIF's - fixed female character wields - Cache packed 525 maps - Updated flo - New runescape login screen + loading bar - Better item rotations - 562 Identitykit[/SPOILER]
[SPOILER="My Super Sexy Updates..Liam Is Jelly <3"] new home custom start for new comers added shops to home [url=http://google.com/runescape-development/google/snippets/406425-pi-perfect-skilling-rewards-spoonfed.html]http://google.com/runescape-development/google/snippets/406425-pi-perfect-skilling-rewards-spoonfed.html[/url] (player achieves a 99, earns a reward in bank) [url=http://google.com/runescape-development/google/tutorials/406625-better-emote-system.html]http://google.com/runescape-development/google/tutorials/406625-better-emote-system.html[/url] (better skillcape emotes) new emotes tab icons adding poision and removing poision from DDS poision saving after log out added Fully working brawlers + effects Treasure Trails Ventrix'd 99% Extreme Potions (Including Super Prayer and Restore Special) better Crafting systems better herblore system added SkillHandler system added death messages *cleaned* anti fire pots (just add the import) major Dupe Fix added 100% chaos tunnels (porta,s enterance to tunnels, portals, exit) range max hit formula re-writen bankx2 fixing duel arena major dupe duel arena match finished bug/dupe fixed stackable bug fixed alchemy Dupe fixed re-writen fletching better yell command (removed: donator, extreme donatr) added helpful commands (::takeitem, ::empty, ::who, ::massnpc, ::infspec, ::giveitem, ::resettask) - Might need to re-arrange the commands thought ;) added korasi special *19780* added dragon claw special (you finish it) added server message system fixed shop major dupe exploit Fix trade X bug fix Saradomin godsword special heal fixed fight caves (you finish the lsat part off, or do you ;)!) block emotes re-writen fixed all item packets dupes close button fix dropdupe fix private messaging fixed (client sided) npchandler mass lag fixed diagonal Attack Fixed clan chat abuse fixed (ex: muted members of clan chat won't be able to talk) administrators cant PK (toggle ON & Off) - [url=http://google.com/runescape-development/google/snippets/374946-pi-admins-cant-pk.html]http://google.com/runescape-development/google/snippets/374946-pi-admins-cant-pk.html[/url] snow globe + snow ball completed added 97% of every single npc on RuneScape (attack/deeath) added balak the pumbler boss added npcs to dag cave pt.2 total In-Game Playtime Hans hands you a Veteran cape after playing for 30 days *add npc to spawn-config* added 99.9% Full enchantment system (sapphire needs to be added ;)) Instant item appearance in wilderness proper mining emotes added birds nests fixed combat styles from the combat triangle (kicking, punching,etc.) saving players on close added sailing teletabs added + correct locations nearly every single god damn dupe fixed <3[/SPOILER]
[SPOILER="General Updates"]The Release has some of the basics like:
[ul][*]Tzhaar Cave + NOW ALL NPCS [*]Pest Control [*]Old Godwars [*]Duel Arena [*]Barrows [*]The classic training zones (except for Rock Crabs Obviously) [*]Same Old bosses [*] You guys should know the basics of a blank PI by now ;)[/ul] [/SPOILER]
